      <title>金多斯称 9 月对欧洲央行决策来说“更方便”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/guindos-says-september-more-convenient-for-ecb-decision-making</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行副行长路易斯·德金多斯表示，欧洲央行在秋季举行的下次管理委员会会议上将能够更好地决定利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/guindos-says-september-more-convenient-for-ecb-decision-making</guid>
